com.b2international.snowowl.terminologymetadata.validation

Interface CodeSystemValidator


  • public interface CodeSystemValidator
    A sample validator interface for CodeSystem. This doesn't really do anything, and it's not a real EMF artifact. It was generated by the org.eclipse.emf.examples.generator.validator plug-in to illustrate how EMF's code generator can be extended. This can be disabled with -vmargs -Dorg.eclipse.emf.examples.generator.validator=false.
